sequenceDiagram
    actor A as Admin
    participant B as Browser
    participant API as PATCH /api/customers/[id]
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Q as BullMQ
    participant W as MikroTik Worker
    participant MT as MikroTik RouterOS

    A->>B: Ubah status pelanggan ke "suspended"
    B->>API: PATCH { status: "suspended" }
    API->>DB: SELECT customer WHERE id=?
    DB-->>API: { pppoeUsername, status: "active" }
    API->>DB: UPDATE customers SET status='suspended'
    DB-->>API: ok
    API->>Q: enqueueSuspendPPPoE({ username })
    API-->>B: 200 { customer, jobId }

    Q->>W: deliver SUSPEND_PPPOE
    W->>MT: /ppp/secret/set disabled=yes [find name=...]
    MT-->>W: ok
    W->>MT: /ppp/active/remove [find name=...]
    MT-->>W: ok (sesi terputus)
    W->>Q: ack
